OL,3,CWatchdog to reinvestigate police over
OL,4,Cdeath of abuse victim
OL,6,FThe police watchdog is reinvestigating
OL,7,Fhow officers handled the case of a
OL,8,Fdomestic abuse victim who died while
OL,9,Freporting an assault.
OL,11,FA previous investigation by the
OL,12,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,13,F(IOPC) found no Lincolnshire Police
OL,14,Fofficers had a case to answer over the
OL,15,Fdeath of 23-year-old Daniela Espirito
OL,16,FSanto in 2020.
