OL,3,CWatchdog to reinvestigate police over
OL,4,Cdeath of abuse victim
OL,6,FBut the watchdog said it would look at
OL,7,Fthe case again "in light of evidence
OL,8,Fthat came out at the inquest and
OL,9,Frepresentations from Ms Santo's
OL,10,Ffamily".
OL,12,FIt said "potentially inappropriate
OL,13,Fcomments" caught on police custody
OL,14,FCCTV would be among the material
OL,15,Flooked at.
OL,17,FMs Santo suffered a fatal cardiac
OL,18,Farrest at her home in Grantham,
OL,19,FLincolnshire, in the early hours of 9
OL,20,FApril 2020.
