OL,3,CWatchdog to reinvestigate police over
OL,4,Cdeath of abuse victim
OL,6,FHer inquest heard she had earlier told
OL,7,Fofficers her partner, Julio Jesus, had
OL,8,Fstrangled and bitten her and broken
OL,9,Fher fingers.
OL,11,FAfter being told to dial the non-
OL,12,Femergency 101 number she died while on
OL,13,Fhold.
OL,15,FThe inquest heard Jesus had been
OL,16,Farrested for a separate assault and
OL,17,Fhad been bailed on the morning of Ms
OL,18,FSanto's death.
