OL,3,CWatchdog to reinvestigate police over
OL,4,Cdeath of abuse victim
OL,6,FHe broke his bail conditions by
OL,7,Freturning to property they shared and
OL,8,Fattacked her.
OL,10,FThe inquest jury found Ms Santo's
OL,11,Fheart condition was triggered by the
OL,12,Femotional distress caused by domestic
OL,13,Fabuse and the assault.
OL,15,FIt found she was unlawfully killed and
OL,16,Fsaid Lincolnshire Police had "missed
OL,17,Fopportunities to safeguard Daniela and
OL,18,Fher children".
OL,20,FThe force later issued an apology to
OL,21,FMs Espirito Santo's family.
