OL,3,CWatchdog to reinvestigate police over
OL,4,Cdeath of abuse victim
OL,6,FThe IOPC conducted an investigation
OL,7,Finto police contact with Ms Santo and
OL,8,FMr Jesus in the 12 months prior to her
OL,9,Fdeath, finding "no indication any
OL,10,Fpolice officer had behaved in a manner
OL,11,Fthat may have breached police
OL,12,Fstandards of professional behaviour
OL,13,Fand would justify bringing
OL,14,Fdisciplinary proceedings".
OL,16,FBut it said the evidence heard at the
OL,17,Finquest meant it was right to
OL,18,Freinvestigate.
