OL,3,CWatchdog to reinvestigate police over
OL,4,Cdeath of abuse victim
OL,6,FIOPC director Emily Barry said: "A
OL,7,Fmatter can only be reinvestigated by
OL,8,Fthe IOPC if there are compelling
OL,9,Freasons to do so and it's in the
OL,10,Fpublic interest. We believe that
OL,11,Fcriteria is met.
OL,13,F"A reinvestigation will enable us to
OL,14,Ffurther scrutinise the issues and make
OL,15,Fdecisions that factor in all of the
OL,16,Fevidence now available, including the
OL,17,Fcustody CCTV footage from 8 April 2020
OL,18,Fthat has come to light and captures
OL,19,Fpotentially inappropriate comments in
OL,20,Frelation to the incident.
