OL,3,CWatchdog to reinvestigate police over
OL,4,Cdeath of abuse victim
OL,6,F"Our re-investigation has begun and is
OL,7,Fbeing conducted by a new investigation
OL,8,Fteam. We will continue to keep Ms
OL,9,FEspirito Santo's family informed of
OL,10,Fthe situation and report the results
OL,11,Fof the new investigation in due
OL,12,Fcourse."
OL,14,FFollowing Ms Santo's death, Jesus was
OL,15,Farrested on suspicion of manslaughter.
OL,17,FHowever, the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,18,F(CPS) said it could not prove "an
OL,19,Fevidential link" between the assault
OL,20,Fand her death and dropped the
OL,21,Fmanslaughter charge.
