OL,6,FInstead he was convicted of two counts
OL,7,Fof assault and spent 10 months in
OL,8,Fprison.
OL,10,FA Lincolnshire Police spokesperson
OL,11,Fsaid it would not comment on the IOPC
OL,12,Finvestigation, but said it was
OL,13,F"cooperating".
